data.description: Don't miss out on this cozy 3 bed 2 bath home. The upper level has 3 bedrooms and one full bathroom. The basement bathroom has a new floor. There is also a large laundry area and family room with a wood burning fireplace in the basement. The yard is fenced in - in back and there are under ground sprinklers. The roof is approximately 1 year old. The smart thermostat, smart ceiling fan in the primary bedroom and the smart switch in the garage will all stay. Work bench in the garage and the security equipment will not stay.
